SEARCH
Package au.csiro.pathling.search.filter

Class FhirFieldNames

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.search.filter.FhirFieldNames
public final class FhirFieldNames extends Object
Centralized constants for FHIR element field names used in search filters.

These constants are used across multiple search matchers to avoid duplication and ensure consistency. All field names follow FHIR naming conventions.
